        10,
        16
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia",
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Churchville%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The village incorporated on September 21, 1852, preserving the original land ownership of Samuel Church.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        5
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Churchville%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "In 1837 the Tonawanda railroad cut through Churchville, accelerating its development.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        11
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
